// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/cl2BzV kisrhombille, written 2023 by jt

// kisrhombille tiling: essentially a checker pattern in barycentric coordinates (orthogonal to triangle).
// https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kisrhombille

// Related: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/dtSBzc kisquadrille

// tags: checker, barycentric, pattern, tiling, euclidean, tesselation, kisrhombille

